An environment setup for raspberry pi rev-B
- rootfs: buildroot
- kernel: linux or linux buildroot
- bootloader: uboot (optional)

Setup environment
- source setenv.sh

# Init development environment
- source setenv.sh
- cd build 

# Kernel build
- make kernel-config
- make kernel

# Buildroot build
- make br-config
- make br
- make br-mmc 

# Uboot build
- make uboot-config
- make uboot
- make uboot-mmc-scr

Output
- stored in build/output
